```

Key gotcha: `@workspace/ui/globals.css` expects many tokens as **raw HSL channels** (like `210 94.4% 32.7%`), not `oklch(...)`, because it does `hsl(var(--token))`.

If you only want overrides in one area, scope them:

```css
.landing-theme {
  --primary: 14 90% 54%;
}
```

Then wrap that section with `<div className="landing-theme">...</div>`.

